nits.com/2013/08/17/gauge/tightandloose/" data-orig-file=3D"https://i0.wp.c=
om/blog.tincanknits.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/tightandloose.jpg?fit=3D=
600%2C400&amp;ssl=3D1" data-orig-size=3D"600,400" data-comments-opened=3D"1=
" data-image-meta=3D"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;=
