<p>Now is the time to re-measure!</p>



<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"once-you-ve-measured-gauge-what-s-the-=
next-step">Once you=E2=80=99ve measured gauge, what=E2=80=99s the next step=
?</h2>



<p>If the gauge of your blocked swatch is exactly the same as the gauge req=
uired by the pattern, you are lucky!&nbsp; You can proceed to start the pat=
tern using the needles you used to make your swatch.</p>



