            <div class=3D"commententry">
                            <p>Hello! I am so excited about your website. A=
nd even more excited that you answer questions.</p>
<p>I am ready to knit my first sweater =E2=80=93 Flax =E2=80=93 and am look=
ing forward to using your tutorials.  (I also couldn=E2=80=99t resist buyin=
g Gramps so that I can learn how to do cardigans. But first things first.)<=
/p>
<p>I have quite a bit of Patons Classic Wool Worsted, so thought I=E2=80=99=
