            <div class=3D"commententry">
                            <p>Thank you, this is very helpful! I made the =
Clayoquot toque to gague for the Trek sweater, but there isn=E2=80=99t enou=
gh colourwork vs. non-colourwork to measure both. Is a combination fine or =
do I do a separate swatch for the solid part?<br>
And I=E2=80=99m off by 1.5 sts=E2=80=A6should I go down just one needle siz=
e or more? (should be 22, I got 23-23.5)<br>
